{"tid":1211930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"準備物資，我地黎個真正嘉年華!","createTime":"2019-06-12T16:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T14:48:03.000Z","uid":57076,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8691712bc3a35056501849d4dc6c48973eb5ccea","tid":1211930,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:54:47.000Z","msg":"嘉年華嚟講<br />\n緊係唔少得食物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4QthZqj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4QthZqj.jpg&h=f6462111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KFQ8mDS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFQ8mDS.jpg&h=0feea366&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藝術黎講，緊係要有油畫，增添豐富色彩!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0MDFcLL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0MDFcLL.jpg&h=7515c658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZ4w3Sr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZ4w3Sr.jpg&h=20e44ebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家想佈置場地，可以用紙皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mk9Etkj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmk9Etkj.jpg&h=c9831187&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vZk0XdF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvZk0XdF.jpg&h=41d24318&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果鍾意潮，仲可以噴髮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hDhKEsC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhDhKEsC.jpg&h=5a96ac5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等我地黎個歡樂嘉年華<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家仲有無咩補充?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a574e9bb3451ae668896108bba4a6